ike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T02:54:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>bu你呀mo 彈彈波即係點解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nBu 你呀mo係潮州話，即係「屌你老母」<br />\n彈彈波據我所聞係廣州D細路自己作<br />\n純粹順口"},{"pid":"a8547a77ddc921e4e5e278608bbdb0a584963779","tid":218920,"uid":109789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T02:57:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點解台灣讀 危險 同大陸讀 危險 個危字唔同聲調？</blockquote><br />\n台灣同大陸一路都有好多不同發音，譬如話「我和你」個「和」字就唔同"},{"pid":"9e9da509e1a8106cf853ddf5a9d0c8899b1f7485","tid":218920,"uid":109789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T02:59:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我唔洗係大陸讀好耐書都精通蝗語啦ching<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁你識唔識方言啊ching"},{"pid":"997760de7b2277142d5733b90bd1e9abd0eba03a","tid":218920,"uid":106363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T03:01:01.000Z","msg":"老司機係咩意思?"},{"pid":"1ddaf3b9ad3070c21626350a485d2f09440b82c4","tid":218920,"uid":109789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T03:03:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>坑爹係咪坑殺老竇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n嚟度「坑」意思係「玩弄，整蠱，陷害」，但係程度冇咁嚴重<br />\n大陸人鍾意自稱自己係「爸爸」或者「爹」，覺得稱自己係人地老豆自己就好巴閉<br />\n所以「坑爹」意思應該係「玩鳩我」<br />\n「你他媽坑爹啊」意思就係「屌你老母玩鳩我」"},{"pid":"088b5fa19daed3c4a047ac426ef9b6c2651d5473","tid":218920,"uid":64607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T03:08:43.000Z","msg":"見D 大陸人講野D語調咁做作就想笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d4020739d65e720e7cf19d17ed7686726d35acd","tid":218920,"uid":109789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T03:09:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>老司機係咩意思?</blockquote><br />\n「老司機」哩個詞來自一個大陸嘅MV，叫「老司機帶帶我」（好似係），個MV就係一個女人向老司機賣弄風騷，想要個司機大佬車佢一程<br />\n依家話嘅「老司機」，就係形容係網上分享av，寫真，同人或者18禁漫畫嘅人<br />\n大概同成人台D ching差唔多"},{"pid":"ad01337c2eae2fb6ac475bfdb4a73da2a45d163a","tid":218920,"uid":109789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T03:10:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>見D 大陸人講野D語調咁做作就想笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有D時候我都忍唔住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a8a9974b5042462edd1e797ed435ed87f59d935","tid":218920,"uid":95155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T03:12:27.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"bc0935ba8c229f835b0179925fba55255426159e","tid":218920,"uid":71579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T03:20:28.000Z","msg":"JJYY啫係點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84c9562325ba5088852756e35aea015e1154b6a5","tid":218920,"uid":95155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T03:40:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"84bd0e4a931f075712b8725b37b4e7a648e281d8","tid":218920,"uid":109789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T04:29:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>皮皮蝦我們走 點解？</blockquote><br />\n皮皮蝦係一種生物，好似係因為一個微博ac 叫「博物雜誌」，介紹唔少嘅罕見生物，皮皮蝦得以介紹而出名<br />\n然後有人整咗張一個人坐住只皮皮蝦嘅圖，配住「皮皮蝦我們走」嘅圖，有少少似D meme，其實冇特別意思，不過係大陸網路嘅gag"},{"pid":"fc1780b5900bf75e88869b156ccdd9f05800bcfe","tid":218920,"uid":92636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T04:40:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>皮皮蝦我們走 點解？</blockquote><br />\n皮皮蝦係一種生物，好似係因為一個微博ac 叫「博物雜誌」，介紹唔少嘅罕見生物，皮皮蝦得以介紹而出名<br />\n然後有人整咗張一個人坐住只皮皮蝦嘅圖，配住「皮皮蝦我們走」嘅圖，有少少似D meme，其實冇特別意思，不過係大陸網路嘅gag</blockquote><br />\n皮皮蝦好似係賴尿蝦？"},{"pid":"6857c0c42541de4a5ae8261ca517e76e1fed1342","tid":218920,"uid":95155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T05:21:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3ee777246c530883f85609c85b48537362085795","tid":218920,"uid":64607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T08:48:54.000Z","msg":"想學台灣國語都唔想學蝗調語，太難聽又顯得自己無文化"},{"pid":"65ed64a555f2a4d5